on rouge la about albemarle corpalbemarle’s active pharmaceutical ingredients apis serve as the cornerstone of many wellknown brands of ethical and otc analgesics and anesthetics we have supplied this marketplace reliably for over  years and can help you grow your business in the generic market focusing on highvalue complicated multiplestep apis served via injectable oral or other delivery systems use our apis or let us conduct exclusive custom synthesis of your apis at any of our multiple cgmp facilitiescompetitors of albemarle corpvettera premier contract development and manufacturing organization cdmo vetter is a global leader in the fill  finish contract manufacturing of aseptically prefilled syringe systems cartridges and vials we are a familyowned independent company with facilities both in germany and the us as read more send an email email sent  products write a reviewbaxter biopharma solutionswith more than  years as a parenterals specialist baxter’s biopharma solutions business offers contract manufacturing formfillfinish services and solutions for injectables designed to meet complex and traditional sterile manufacturing challenges we are a leading contract manufacturer read more send an email email sent  products write a reviewspi pharmaspi pharma is a global leader serving over  countries in the manufacture and marketing of antacid actives excipients drug delivery systems for tablets soft gel capsules fastdissolve technologies chewables lozenges and a variety of other patientfriendly dosage forms spi also  products write a review×rate and review albemarle corp click on a star to rate this companyrating is requiredyour associationcustomerpartnersupplierother name title company post anonymouslyyour comments when writing a review please adhere to the review guidelines thanks for submitting your review of albemarle corp well email you as soon as its published typically within  hours we really value your contributions and so does our community of business pr